= Special Criminal Status Revoked

Merlyn Rees, Secretary of State for Northern Ireland has revoked Special Category Status for those sentenced for crimes relating to civil violence.

Rumours have spread that the British government plans to intern members of the IRA and INLA in newly constructed blocks in Long Kesh.
